data.description: Welcome to 8037 Reid Ave., a meticulously updated 3-bed, 2-bath home offering remarkable living. Enjoy the freedom with no HOA or CDD fees, bringing your boat, RV, and trailer hassle-free. Inside, discover a transformed interior with new HVAC, elegant white kitchen cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Stylish vanities, new fixtures, and luxury vinyl plank flooring add modern charm. Fresh paint, new windows, and doors enhance efficiency and security. Ample parking includes a 2-car carport and driveway. The fully fenced backyard offers privacy. Conveniently located near Walmart Super Center (4.2 miles), I-95 (1.1 miles), and Powerhouse Gym (2.6 miles). This updated home, free of HOA and CDD fees, is a rare find. Schedule a showing today! All information pertaining to the property is deemed reliable, but not guaranteed. Information to be verified by the Buyer.
